<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id4d5d1301-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d" identifier="/us/usc/t34/s50106"><num value="50106">§ 50106.</num><heading> Prohibition of land acquisition</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">No funds provided under this chapter shall be used for land acquisition.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id4d5d1302-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d">(<ref href="/us/pl/98/473/tII/s609R">Pub. L. 98–473, title II, § 609R</ref>, <date date="1984-10-12">Oct. 12, 1984</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/98/2106">98 Stat. 2106</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id4d5d1303-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id4d5d1304-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I76" topic="codification" id="id4d5d1305-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Codification</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section was formerly classified to <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s10506">section 10506 of Title 42</ref>, The Public Health and Welfare, prior to editorial reclassification and renumbering as this section.</p>
</note>
